d by ISC Ca2+ waves. Neonatal IHCs thus spontaneously generate electrical and Ca2+ activity, which is enhanced and largely synchronized by activity of ISCs of K{\"{o}}lliker's organ indicating two sources of spontaneous activity in the developing auditory system.},
